      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="  Establish  an internal menu, probably electronic, from which employees pick their orders  for common low value items. This kind of catalogue can be used in conjunction  with purchasing via purchasing card. Restrict purchasing to catalogue items  from recognized suppliers to ensure economies of scale are gained by bulk  buying and the number of suppliers used is kept under control."/>
